the_residence_act_allowed_the president_to_select a location_within_maryland_as_far_east_as_the_anacostia_river .
however , washington_shifted_the_federal_territory_'s borders_to_the_southeast_in_order_to_include_the_city_of alexandria_at_the_district_'s_southern_tip .
in_1791 , congress_amended_the_residence act_to_approve_the_new_site , including_territory_ceded_by_virginia .
