until_1890 , the_u.s . census_bureau_counted_the_city_of_washington , georgetown , and_unincorporated_portions_of_washington_county_as_three_separate_areas .
the data provided_in_this_article_from_before_1890_are_calculated_as_if_the_district_of_columbia_were a single_municipality_as_it_is_today .
population_data for each specific_area prior_to_1890_are_available .
